What are the goals of the project? 

recognise facial emotion in:
	
	static image
		face centered
		face anywhere
		multiple faces
	
	video feed
		
to be recognised facial emotions:
  
  happy
  calm
  sad
  
  angry
  surprised
  confused
  ...

What are possible steps to achieve these goals? 

-preprocessing e.g. noise reduction, histogram equalization, conversion to grayscale, edge detection
-recognise faces and isolate them
-extract feature points in each face
-classify feature points to detect emotion


What are the risks and assumptions? 


Write down open questions!

